"tid":694182,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"420952d76cb40f76447b989a32306a1ab57abb8f","tid":694182,"uid":46595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T09:57:58.000Z","msg":"明買明賣者......<br />\n你都可以唔揀呢D工架麻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T09:58:38.000Z","msg":"邊有得揀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:19:39.000Z","msg":"你做緊咩工，政府定私人企業"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:31:53.000Z","msg":"NGO"},{"pid":"488e3854ba9c9527f235aa9bccd46a27ef16520d","tid":694182,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d443f2fd2feb159af84aba3f072a56ef17093553","tid":694182,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f202bfdda5d0624262e5aed4143650bec8cedb2e","tid":694182,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"da483245a32bd3564ecd28e2b379a5d5c1cd206b","tid":694182,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T09:58:38.000Z","msg":"邊有得揀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:19:39.000Z","msg":"你做緊咩工，政府定私人企業"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:31:53.000Z","msg":"NGO"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"正啦"},{"pid":"5adeb0196d186bac67cd445df157d784356df00e","tid":694182,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:26:56.000Z","msg":"【418僱傭條例課室】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先要同大家澄清一個香港打工仔女都聽過的傳聞：<br />\n【做兼職，乜保障都無？】<br />\n<br />\n錯！<br />\n<br />\n＊＊就算係兼職，只要你有返工，你都有以下待遇<br />\n1) 受工傷保障。有工傷意外，一樣有放工傷病假同賠償。<br />\n2) 唔可以低過最低工資時薪$32.5。 ＊＊<br />\n<br />\n附錄<br />\n現行勞工法例（即係僱傭條例）裡面，無介定點樣先係兼職。<br />\n不過就講明附合「連續性契約」即係俗稱為4.18，就享有一般全職的勞工保障及福利。<br />\n  <br />\n4.18 - 連續性契約<br />\n1) 連續為同一老闆工作滿4星期或以上<br />\n2) 每星期工時不少於18小時<br />\n<br />\n咁睇好似唔夠具體，比個例子大家啦：<br />\n陳師奶做兼職辦公室清潔<br />\n每日返4小時，每星期返5日，即係每星期返20小時<br />\n而佢又已經做超過3個月<br />\n咁五一勞動節呢日呢，就可以好似其他全職員工咁，有假放兼有一日人工！就算叫「兼職」都有全職待遇！<br />\n<br />\n所以話，有咩懷疑比人食夾棍、計少左福利，唔好諗，即刻打黎2770 8668搵工會傾下！<br />\n<br />\n#五一 #勞動節 #418 #零散工 #兼職 #假期錢 #食夾棍<br />\n<br />\n======================================="},{"pid":"6d94c1b6c02bfaab1530f0b3e5b978597d55a122","tid":694182,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T07:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14b3568c97ca2d413bff5d1f6c6c6ba551ea72d","tid":694182,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ffd2a013d1eca974a01463469588ceb49066c14","tid":694182,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:36:54.000Z","msg":"其實外判都係政府搞先<br />\n所以政府想負少啲責任都唔係今日嘅事啦"},{"pid":"ab097f1d9843013edbe66162756e6e1a883b7edc","tid":694182,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T10:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}